# K7 Design

**Brand**: Cinematic. Yours. Understated. Dark-first cinema UI; content (posters, covers) is the hero.

- Tokens only: copper accent via CSS variables, never hard-coded hex
- Typography: Epilogue (headings), Manrope (body)
- WCAG AA minimum; 44px touch targets on mobile
- Adapt per context (desktop, mobile, couch) - do not just shrink desktop layouts

## Avoid (AI slop)

Neon/cyan-purple gradients, glassmorphism, gradient text, hero metrics, identical card grids, nested cards, generic fonts (Inter/Roboto), bounce easing, gray-on-color text, pure black/white.

## Principles

Content first. Cinematic restraint. Tokens over hard-codes. Every context first-class. Accessible by default.

